messages.everyone:
**Shush!**

If you want to mention a specific group, please use their role.
If you really meant to mention everyone then continue on with your day, otherwise you should feel bad about annoying these nice people.
messages.welcome:
**Hello there!** Welcome to the server!
This server is for the most elite of the elite so you must confirm your identity first.
To confirm your identity please reply with a message or messages about you: who you are, who invited you, why you are gonna be here and so on.
Your greatness will then be put up for review by one of our overloards.

Thank you,
	*beepus*
